 het vervolledigen van uw gegevens? Bekijk de <a href=\"https://studietoelagen.be/stel-je-vraag-aan-studietoelagen\">verschillende mogelijkheden om hulp te krijgen</a>.</p>","en":"<p>If you think you are eligible for a study grant, please submit your <a href=\"https://daf.vlaanderen.be\">application for a study grant (online)</a>.</p><p>If you would like to have more information and guidance, please contact the student services of your educational institution.</p><p> </p><p>If you want the Study Grants Division to start up a file for you and examine whether you qualify for a study grant, you can set up a profile in the digital portal on the website <a href=\"http://www.studietoelagen.be\">studietoelagen.be</a>:</p><ul><li>you enter your contact details and bank account number;</li><li>you indicate that you want a file (either only the current academic year, or every year as long as you study);</li><li>you can give access to a parent who lives at the same address to follow up the file</li></ul><p>Please note: in higher education, the student is the person entitled to a possible study grant and is also responsible for arranging the file. Only the student can set up his profile.</p><p>As soon as the file has been started, you will receive an e-mail with the request to check and confirm your data and send additional information if necessary. You’ll be informed as soon as the file is being processed.</p><p>If you would like to have more information and guidance, please contact the student services of your educational institution or call the free number 1700.</p>","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>Als je wilt dat Studietoelagen voor jou een dossier opstart en onderzoekt of je in aanmerking komt voor een studietoelage, dan kan je in het <a href=\"https://loket-studietoelagen-app.onderwijs-apps.vlaanderen.be/dossier\">digitaal loket</a> op de website www.studietoelagen.be jouw profiel instellen vanaf 2 juni voorafgaand aan het academiejaar waarvoor je een toelage wenst:</p><